====================================================================================================
This directory contains tools and makefile scripts that are not "runtime".

The top level "include" directory contains make scripts that are included during "makefile" processing.
The top level scripts directory are scripts that are executed either internally (only) or exported
for users (possibly without a suffix).
Python utilities are in the python directory.
Major tools are in their own subdirectories built normally, starting with ocpigen.
The cdkutils directory is a CD++ library potentially use by multiple tools.
